title: #92Noon! HS Football is BACK!!!
description: Cheers to high school football, including a "whistle stop" shoutout during the first hour, lamenting Anthony Barr's injury, Uncle Norv joins at 10am, followed by Charch's fantasy pickup joint, and Aaron Gleeman hangs out for final hour!
